{
  "stem": "18258.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And we knew that we as Jews were in mortal danger.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And we were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Within three days-- Monday morning-- the Nazis came to our apartment, pulled my parents out of their beds.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "They didn't give mother even a chance to put on a robe.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "In her nightgown, they pulled her out of bed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And my dad, who was sedated because of war injuries, he didn't even know for 10 minutes what happened.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "I had opened the door because I was sleeping in, in the front door.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And there came two SS and two SA men.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "First thing which entered the door when I got it finally open was a handgun, followed by a black-- by a black sleeve.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "And then the, the four guys came in, ransacked the entire apartment, went in, threw everything out of the linen closets and the closets out on the floor looking for whatever they could use-- every document, money.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Whatever they found, they confiscated.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then they marched my dad and myself down across the street to our store and did the same there, ransacked the store.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "But the sewing operators-- the sewing machine operators were already waiting in front of the store because we started our store at 7:00.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "These people came at 6:00 to our apartment Monday morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And whatever money they had found upstairs in our apartment-- there was quite a sum because we had prepared bills to be paid Monday morning.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They took that.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They left us the bills, but they took the money.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they handed a good part of it out to the sewing machine operators, telling them, oh, that Jews was exploiting you anyway.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "There you have victory bonuses.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And that was our very first experience in our own family.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
